values: The journal of Mia Tyler is FRIENDS ONLY!!! I will not add civillans and such nor people who diss Mia, her family, or anything like that. Comment nicely and I will probably add you back! ;-) [Oh yes, just to make things a whole heck of a lot clearer, this is NOT really Mia Tyler's journal. Sorry to burst your bubble, but this is part of a game. A role-playing game as a matter of fact. So don't email or comment saying things like 'Is this realy Mia Tyler?' Because it's not. So, just to get the point across. AND if your still confused, here's a lovely community which explains everything: Thanks!:-)]
